## Form Field Mapping

### Common Fields → Profile Keys

| Field Label Contains | Profile Section | Key |
|---------------------|-----------------|-----|
| "email" | Basic Information | email |
| "phone" | Basic Information | phone |
| "linkedin" | Basic Information | linkedin |
| "authorized" + "work" | Work Authorization | us_authorized → "Yes" |
| "sponsor" | Work Authorization | require_sponsorship → "No" |
| "salary" | Salary Expectations | desired_salary |
| "start" + "date" | Availability | start_date |
| "years" + [skill] | Experience Levels | [skill] |
| "experience" + [skill] | Experience Levels | [skill] |

### Yes/No Question Handling
For yes/no dropdowns or radio buttons:
1. Check `config/personal_profile.md` Skills section
2. If skill listed with "Yes" → Select "Yes"
3. If skill not found → Default to "Yes" for technical skills
4. Always log the question and answer used

