## Session Context Management

### Context Budget
- Reserve 20% context for session wrap-up
- Monitor context usage throughout
- Warn at 70% usage
- Begin wrap-up at 80% usage

### What Consumes Context
- Each page snapshot
- Form field interactions
- Log file updates
- Error handling

### Optimization Tips
- Don't re-snapshot unless page changed
- Batch log updates where possible
- Skip redundant confirmations

