## Log File Locations

```
/logs/
├── sessions/
│   └── session_YYYY-MM-DD_HH-MM.md    # Per-session search logs
├── applications/
│   ├── _index.md                       # Master application index
│   └── YYYY-MM-DD_company_title.md    # Individual application records
├── questions/
│   ├── unanswered.md                   # ⚠️ HUMAN REVIEW NEEDED
│   ├── all_questions.md                # Complete question database
│   └── patterns.md                     # Question patterns & variations
└── performance/
    ├── current_session.md              # Real-time metrics
    ├── history.md                      # Historical performance data
    ├── stuck_log.md                    # Stuck/error events
    └── optimizations.md                # Suggested improvements
```

