## User Commands

### Start Applying
Triggers: "apply to jobs", "start applying", "job hunt", "find jobs"
Action: Execute full workflow from Phase 1

### Quick Apply
Triggers: "apply to next X jobs", "apply to X more"
Action: Skip search, apply to next X visible Easy Apply jobs

### Status Check
Triggers: "status", "how many applied", "progress"
Action: Report current session statistics

### Stop
Triggers: "stop", "pause", "end session"
Action: Complete current application, finalize logs, end

### Review Questions
Triggers: "what questions", "unanswered", "need my input"
Action: Display contents of logs/questions/unanswered.md

